headline: Royal Caribbean (RCL): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q1 Earnings?
summary: What a fantastic six months it’s been for Royal Caribbean. Shares of the company have skyrocketed 50.6%, setting a new 52-week high of $342.19. This was partly thanks to its solid quarterly results, and the performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
